Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ih, gatinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Um bom tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,É
